snippet.title: Michael Jackson : The Experience (2010) Nintendo DS Gameplay in HD (DeSmuME)
snippet.description:
Game name - Michael Jackson : The Experience

Console - Nintendo DS
Game Release - 2010-11-06
Publisher - Ubisoft
Genre - Rhythm


Michael Jackson: The Experience is a Rhythm video game published by Ubisoft released on November 6th, 2010 for the Nintendo DS.


DeSmuME X432R Settings
Renderer - OpenGL×4(1024×768)
SoftRasterizer Option
Unrealistically High-Precision Color Interpolation - On
Enable Edge Marking - On
Enable Fog - On
Enable Textures - On
Enable TXT Hack - On
Enable LINE Hack - On
Enable Anti-Aliasing - On
LCDs Layout - Horizontal
Windows Size - 4×
Sound Settings
Synchronous- On
Synch Method - N


My PC Specs
OS - Windows 10 Home
CPU - Intel Core i7-7700K @ 4.20GHz 4.20 GHz
GPU - NVIDIA® GeForce® GTX 1070
RAM - 16.0 GB
